title: Jimmy Fitzpatrick Poaches Desert Airfield with Friends
description: Deep in California’s barren Mohave desert, known for it’s incredibly harsh environment and scorching heart, Metal Mulisha rider Jimmy Fitzpatrick poached an airfield at an undisclosed location, along with a team of death defying thrill seekers including aviation stunt pilot Melissa Andrzejeswki and stuntman Andy Lewis, to pull of a one of kind project.
